'''山茱萸科'''（学名：Cornaceae）是[[山茱萸目|山茱萸目]]的一个[[科|科]]。广泛分布于北温带。包括[[八角枫属|八角枫属]]和[[山茱萸屬|山茱萸屬]]兩屬約85種灌木、喬木<ref name="Christenhusz-Byng2016">{{cite journal | author1 = Christenhusz, M. J. M. | author2 = Byng, J. W. | lastauthoramp = yes | year = 2016 | title = The number of known plants species in the world and its annual increase | journal = Phytotaxa | volume = 261 | pages = 201–217 | url = http://biotaxa.org/Phytotaxa/article/download/phytotaxa.261.3.1/20598 | doi = 10.11646/phytotaxa.261.3.1 | issue = 3 | publisher = Magnolia Press | access-date = 2019-03-14 | archive-date = 2019-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190626021838/https://biotaxa.org/Phytotaxa/article/download/phytotaxa.261.3.1/20598 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=Kubitzki>Kubitzki, K. (2004). Cornaceae. In ''The Families and Genera of Vascular Plants Volume 6: Flowering Plants: Dicotyledons: Celastrales, Oxidales, Rosales, Cornales, Ericales'' (Kubitzki, ed.). Springer-Verlag, New York.</ref>。

==下级分类==
本科包括以下属：
* ''Acuba'' Link, 1822 = [[桃叶珊瑚属|桃叶珊瑚属]] ''Aucuba'' Thunb., 1783
* [[单性茱萸属|单性茱萸属]] ''Afrocrania'' (Harms) Hutch. ≡ [[山茱萸属|山茱萸属]]  Cornus L.
* ''Alangiophyllum'' Potbury, 1935
* ''Alangioxylon'' N.Awasthi, 1969
* [[八角枫属|八角枫属]] ''Alangium'' Lam.
* ''Aukuba'' Thunb ex Koehne, 1893
* [[桃叶珊瑚属|桃叶珊瑚属]] ''Aukuba'' Thunberg, 1784
* [[边沁兰属|边沁兰属]] ''Benthamia''
* [[灯台树属|灯台树属]] ''Bothrocaryum'' (Koehne) Pojark. ≡ [[山茱萸属|山茱萸属]]  Cornus L.
* ''Browniea'' S.R.Manchester & L.J.Hickey, 2007
* [[草茱萸属|草茱萸属]] ''Chamaepericlimenum'' Asch. & Graebn.
* ''Clavaecutis'' W.Schneider, 2004
* ''Cornophyllum'' Newberry, 1895
* ''Cornoxylon'' H.Conwentz ex H.Vater, 1884
* [[山茱萸属|山茱萸属]] ''Cornus'' L.
* ''Davidoidea'' T.Johnson, 1937
* [[四照花属|四照花属]] ''Dendrobenthamia'' Hutch. ≡ [[山茱萸属|山茱萸属]]  Cornus L.
* ''Diacaecarpium'' Endl., 1839
* [[毛八角枫属|毛八角枫属]] ''Diacecarpium'' Hassk.
* ''Diplomastixia'' F.Kirchheimer, 1935
* [[盘花狗木属|盘花狗木属]] ''Discocrania'' (Harms) M.Král ≡ [[山茱萸属|山茱萸属]]  Cornus L.
* ''Dunstania'' E.M.Reid & M.E.J.Chandler, 1933
* ''Eomastixia'' M.E.J.Chandler, 1926
* ''Fadgenia'' Lindl.
* ''Ganitrocera'' F.Kirchheimer, 1935
* ''Grieselinia'' Endl., 1840
* ''Griselinia''
* ''Hartzia'' Nikitin, 1965
* ''Hironoia'' M.Takahashi, P.R.Crane & S.R.Manchester, 2002
* ''Kaliphora''
* ''Lanfrancia'' E.M.Reid & M.E.J.Chandler, 1933
* ''Langtonia'' E.M.Reid & M.E.J.Chandler, 1933
* ''Mastixioidea'' Kirchheimer, 1936
* ''Mastixioidiocarpum'' R.A.Scott, 1954
* ''Mastixiopsis'' F.Kirchheimer, 1936
* ''Muzquizoxylon'' Estrada-Ruiz et al., 2010
* ''Nyssoidea'' M.E.J.Chandler, 1962
* ''Nyssoxylon'' E.Mädel, 1959
* ''Palaeonyssa'' E.M.Reid & M.E.J.Chandler, 1933
* ''Paleodavidia'' S.Miki, 1956
* ''Platymastixia'' F.Kirchheimer, 1935
* ''Plexiplica'' F.Kirchheimer, 1936
* ''Portnallia'' M.E.J.Chandler, 1961
* ''Protonyssa'' E.M.Reid & M.E.J.Chandler, 1933
* ''Retinomastixia'' F.Kirchheimer, 1938
* ''Svida'' Opiz
* [[梾木属|梾木属]] ''Swjda Opiz
* ''Tectocarya'' F.Kirchheimer, 1935
* [[欧瑞木属|欧瑞木属]] ''Thelycrania'' (Dumort.) Fourr. ≡ [[山茱萸属|山茱萸属]]  Cornus L.
* ''Toricellia''
* ''Torricellia''
* ''Tsukada'' J.A.Wolfe & W.Wehr, 1987
* ''Xylomastixia'' F.Kirchheimer, 1938

